summary: For Blue, Blue Skies - Dredfulhapiness - Spider-Man - All Media Types [Archive of Our Own]
body:
For Blue, Blue Skies— AO3

For Blue, Blue Skies - Dredfulhapiness - Spider-Man - All Media Types [Archive of Our Own]

Summary:

Mathematically, one of two things should have happened when Peter and Harry became friends. The first solution was that Peter’s negative social status would bring Harry down. The second solution was that Harry’s overwhelming social prowess would make Peter popular enough that Flash Thompson would invite him to a party.

(Previously titled ‘I Wish We Met Before They Convinced You Life Is War)

summary: Ultimate Jessica Drew was my teenage self’s non-binary comic book girlfriend and I recently had the realization that I am...
body: Ultimate Jessica Drew was my teenage self’s non-binary comic book girlfriend and I recently had the realization that I am exactly the same age as RIPeter. So I was compelled to draw Ultimate Jess how she would appear in Into the Spider-verse. For some reason Jess being a blond is weirder to me than RIPeter being one….
